# Factual Information

## History of Flight

Prior to flight | Preflight or dispatch event

## Pilot Information

Certificate: | Airline transport; Flight instructor
--- | ---
Age: | 78
Airplane Rating(s): | Single-engine land; Single-engine sea; Multi-engine land; Multi-engine sea
Seat Occupied: | Left
Other Aircraft Rating(s): | None
Restraint Used: | 3-point
Instrument Rating(s): | Airplane
Second Pilot Present: | No
Instructor Rating(s): | Airplane multi-engine; Airplane single-engine; Instrument airplane
Toxicology Performed: | No
Medical Certification: | Class 2 With waivers/limitations
Last FAA Medical Exam: | December 17, 2013
Occupational Pilot: | No
Last Flight Review or Equivalent: | July 29, 2014
